claim.claim-text:
1. A semiconductor package structure comprising:
a leadframe;
an interposer disposed on the leadframe, the interposer comprising a plurality of dielectric layers including at least (i) a first dielectric layer and (ii) a second dielectric layer;
a semiconductor device disposed on the interposer; and
a capacitor that is embedded within the interposer, wherein the capacitor is formed using at least (i) a first conductive area disposed on the first dielectric layer and (ii) a second conductive area disposed on the second dielectric layer.
